{"tid":1378684,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢見到有人用油 小弟有一計將油作用最大化","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:26:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T16:40:06.000Z","uid":156237,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1d67c7dfd20dad995f14236f9a814365b078219a","tid":1378684,"uid":156237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:26:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zajr4XJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzajr4XJ.png&h=b7faa691&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cyvOyQ4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcyvOyQ4.png&h=05cb0f85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n發夢到人揸住啲油，又唔知點用，我心生一計！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">油彈！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果掉得中，又可以搞到啲狗油立立，增加負擔。<br />\n<br />\n如果掉唔中，狗嘅推進路線一定會變滑，難以衝嚟咬我地，甚至仆街。<br />\n<br />\n最後當油量到一定程度，加少少火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n製作時間短，又可到場製作！"},{"pid":"c87b0eb72c7b5ab7b2c78826f034e2ec60dc292b","tid":1378684,"uid":156237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:27:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"524bc0abd5e1543551c6988ed71c54314196f181","tid":1378684,"uid":156237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:28:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cede93a7de6ba76357080bed97f4204989f94c07","tid":1378684,"uid":278524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:30:05.000Z","msg":"食油好似好難點火<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a995ea2a706571573cdaff39d56310e19a5235","tid":1378684,"uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:31:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3057fc58975d7879f2d35a12f54279687e8345","tid":1378684,"uid":199902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc